return ['messages'=>['093dc2c131b4962f56389797f15d725c'=>'And it is an exploration that I want to make. I want to experiment with my body, with the camera, play with the explicit, with the suggestive… See what lighting, what framing, what poses make the photograph go to one side or the other of the scale and find that middle point of balance. Because I firmly believe (and I have seen it in the work of other artists and I have done it when I work with other artists) that explicit photographs can be made, and these can be completely artistic, without being pornographic or vulgar at all, worthy of being in galleries.   ','0a6d70580008c720d1847b9181d01203'=>'So, that\'s my situation. I don\'t want to take sensual photographs that just say "hey, I\'m sexy," but I do believe that artistic photographs can have a strong erotic charge without taking away from the artistic component, and I want to achieve that in my self-portraits. ','0b00c718dead5692024c9d07e4e40c01'=>'https://marianaerato.local/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/DSC09608-scaled.jpg','1cf0fb801ee0950ff95d8f238874588c'=>'https://marianaerato.local/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/DSC09600-scaled.jpg','1eaad5dbb5d80efd4300dec2c45a70d2'=>'Continuing with the topic of self-portraits and whether eroticism can be artistic, there is something that happens to me, and I have become more aware of it over time. I am still in the process of analyzing it, so I may not explain it in the best way, but I will try. ','1f4001216896cfb0817fccdb0c652f1c'=>'https://marianaerato.local/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/DSC09647-scaled.jpg','41c01e4f62e587fd595da95c16cb5e01'=>'https://marianaerato.local/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/DSC09642-scaled.jpg','53c2523d279fe03d0c1a494396bbb373'=>'I have a lot of references, I have the space at home, and I have my body to explore…','57d76e0a44bef18a7400328088c50199'=>'I feel that it is much easier for me to capture the eroticism and beauty of others than my own. When it comes to myself, I find it difficult not to see it forced, too posed, or falling into the obvious. I think that in part I find a refuge in taking photos of others and discovering those parts of each one, to, in some way, escape from looking for my own.','606dec16201f2f752837e746d9f43ed0'=>'https://marianaerato.local/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/DSC09637-scaled.jpg','6365ebe9f8921b734644780d3aa7cdde'=>'https://marianaerato.local/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/DSC09620-scaled.jpg','6cf1066c4ea1495b9c4693b34715d05a'=>'https://marianaerato.local/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/DSC09607-scaled.jpg','75f5bad14b8382c972743c34011afe27'=>'https://marianaerato.local/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/DSC09603-scaled.jpg','7f06c95b9f4f097937cccb9296512a27'=>'https://marianaerato.local/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/DSC09639-scaled.jpg','839cd1e2f922a8315619d7300e4364f5'=>'I can\'t manage to take an erotic photo that I can see and think has an important artistic component.','882a1548f807025c1e3f0a69c4153d55'=>'The other day I woke up at 6 in the morning (which is not normal for me), to wait for the perfect light to enter my living room so I could take photos with a brown leather armchair I found on the street the day before.','8966d13e6e86e799ce178fafe46e8d63'=>'https://marianaerato.local/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/DSC09596-scaled.jpg','90b06ecbdd9b284d972556b224d21479'=>'https://marianaerato.local/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/DSC09623-scaled.jpg','983839458fd3d23c2b8ef3451fc97ac5'=>'That middle ground.','9b6704ec970e9d63f735e672eac4bace'=>'It happens to me that with the photographs I take of myself (self-portraits), I feel that I cannot reach a middle point between the erotic and artistic charge that they have.','Creo que cuando esas fotos tienen una carga sensual o erótica, es de una forma un poco burda y obvia, lo cual le resta esa aura o ese componente etereo que hace que se acerque más a una representación artística (según mi punto de vista, claro está). Y por el contrario, cuando sí que tienen ese componente (que es la minoría de las veces, en mi opinión), es porque suelen estar más orientado hacia la nostalgia y pierden el toque de erotismo.'=>'I think that when these photos have a sensual or erotic charge, it is in a somewhat crude and obvious way, which takes away that aura or ethereal component that makes it closer to an artistic representation (in my opinion, of course). And on the contrary, when they do have that component (which is the minority of times, in my opinion), it is because they tend to be more oriented towards nostalgia and lose the touch of eroticism. ','El otro día me desperté a las 6 de la mañana (cosa que no es normal en mí), para esperar que la luz perfecta entrara en mi salón y poder hacerme fotos con un sillón de cuero marrón que encontré en la calle el día anterior.'=>'The other day I woke up at 6 in the morning (which is not normal for me), to wait for the perfect light to enter my living room so I could take photos with a brown leather armchair I found on the street the day before.','Entonces, esa es mi situación. No quiero hacer fotografías sensuales que solo digan “hola, soy sexy”, pero sí que creo que las fotografías artísticas pueden tener una fuerte carga erótica sin que esta le reste el componente artístico, y quiero conseguirlo en mis autorretratos.'=>'So, that\'s my situation. I don\'t want to take sensual photographs that just say "hey, I\'m sexy," but I do believe that artistic photographs can have a strong erotic charge without taking away from the artistic component, and I want to achieve that in my self-portraits. ','Ese punto medio.'=>'That middle ground.','Gracias siempre por su apoyo ❤️'=>'Thank you always for your support ❤️','Hacerme una foto erótica, que yo pueda ver y piensar que tiene un componente artístico importante, no lo consigo.'=>'I can\'t manage to take an erotic photo that I can see and think has an important artistic component.','Justo cuando la luz estaba en su momento, me di cuenta de que había perdido el control remoto que utilizo para hacerme los autorretratos, por lo que tuve que improvisar, lo que resultó en una pelea con el enfoque, pero en fin… ahí van los resultados:'=>'Just when the light was right, I realized I had lost the remote control I use to take my self-portraits, so I had to improvise, which resulted in a fight with the focus, but anyway… here are the results:','Me sucede, que con las fotografías que me realizo a mí misma (los autorretratos), siento que no consigo llegar a un punto medio entre la carga erótica y la carga artística que estos tengan.'=>'It happens to me that with the photographs I take of myself (self-portraits), I feel that I cannot reach a middle point between the erotic and artistic charge that they have.','Mientras tanto, pueden comentarme sus opiniones por mensajes y así poder tener una perspectiva más amplia al respecto.'=>'In the meantime, you can tell me your opinions via messages so I can have a broader perspective on the matter.','Puedes acompañarme en este proceso, y podemos evidenciar entre todxs los resultados que vaya obteniendo.'=>'You can accompany me in this process, and we can all demonstrate the results I obtain.','Siento que estas fotos se acercan un poco más a lo que quiero lograr, pero todavía me queda mucho camino por recorrer.'=>'I feel like these photos are a little closer to what I want to achieve, but I still have a long way to go.','Siento que se me hace muchísimo más fácil capturar el erotismo y belleza de los demás que el propio. Me cuesta, cuando se trata de mí misma, no verlo forzado, demasiado posado, o cayendo en la obviedad.. Creo que en parte encuentro un refugio en hacerle fotos a otrxs y descubrir esas partes de cada uno, para, de alguna manera, huir de buscar las mías propias.'=>'I feel that it is much easier for me to capture the eroticism and beauty of others than my own. When it comes to myself, I find it difficult not to see it forced, too posed, or falling into the obvious. I think that in part I find a refuge in taking photos of others and discovering those parts of each one, to, in some way, escape from looking for my own.','Siguiendo con el tema de los autorretratos y el de si puede ser artístico lo erótico, hay algo que me pasa, y me he ido haciendo más consciente de ello con el tiempo. Aún estoy en proceso de analizarlo, así que es posible que no lo explique de la mejor manera, pero voy a intentarlo.'=>'Continuing with the topic of self-portraits and whether eroticism can be artistic, there is something that happens to me, and I have become more aware of it over time. I am still in the process of analyzing it, so I may not explain it in the best way, but I will try. ','Tengo muchas referencias, tengo el espacio en casa, y tengo mi cuerpo para explorar…'=>'I have a lot of references, I have the space at home, and I have my body to explore…','Y es una exploración que quiero realizar. Quiero experimentar con mi cuerpo, con la cámara, jugar con lo explícito, con lo sugerente… Ver qué iluminación, qué encuadres, qué poses hacen que la fotografía se vaya hacia un lado o al otro de la balanza e ir encontrando ese punto medio de equilibrio. Porque creo firmemente (y lo he visto en trabajos de otros artistas y lo he realizado cuando trabajo con otros artistas), que se pueden hacer fotografías explícitas, y éstas pueden ser completamente artísticas, sin caer en que sean pornográficas o vulgares en absoluto, dignas de estar en galerías. '=>'And it is an exploration that I want to make. I want to experiment with my body, with the camera, play with the explicit, with the suggestive… See what lighting, what framing, what poses make the photograph go to one side or the other of the scale and find that middle point of balance. Because I firmly believe (and I have seen it in the work of other artists and I have done it when I work with other artists) that explicit photographs can be made, and these can be completely artistic, without being pornographic or vulgar at all, worthy of being in galleries.   ','a56b4c039c438a5a08f18fb17477aba6'=>'https://marianaerato.local/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/DSC09610-scaled.jpg','ab18eed86f34acca76df98a869feda48'=>'https://marianaerato.local/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/DSC09644-scaled.jpg','b8bd4cba32761fa0fecd61debe42f209'=>'Thank you always for your support ❤️','ca85c7bde4202d96e757ad999e57e944'=>'In the meantime, you can tell me your opinions via messages so I can have a broader perspective on the matter.','dd47ca21f3723f01ea469fc9c2b6fe9c'=>'https://marianaerato.local/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/DSC09602-scaled.jpg','dd6f2e008ddc1adecccba484244806f4'=>'You can accompany me in this process, and we can all demonstrate the results I obtain.','de3c00b974345511b41ed5c9e3337241'=>'I feel like these photos are a little closer to what I want to achieve, but I still have a long way to go.','e1746dc453b0ed1ee408c8d55f965ca7'=>'https://marianaerato.local/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/DSC09606-scaled.jpg','e3da1b07b567cb2e43277abccecfb02c'=>'https://marianaerato.local/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/DSC09626-scaled.jpg','e4b293f18091cd771e36cdaa8bd9a64e'=>'I think that when these photos have a sensual or erotic charge, it is in a somewhat crude and obvious way, which takes away that aura or ethereal component that makes it closer to an artistic representation (in my opinion, of course). And on the contrary, when they do have that component (which is the minority of times, in my opinion), it is because they tend to be more oriented towards nostalgia and lose the touch of eroticism. ','ed5192c85578e5d03afed1bbe66c9ddc'=>'Just when the light was right, I realized I had lost the remote control I use to take my self-portraits, so I had to improvise, which resulted in a fight with the focus, but anyway… here are the results:','f4e5d13d9d00436f8bcc4f2081ef1e5b'=>'https://marianaerato.local/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/DSC09618-scaled.jpg','f5e0c00b04e883783751449afb509602'=>'https://marianaerato.local/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/DSC09601-scaled.jpg','h